&lt;p&gt;Entra ID configuration&amp;#58; users, groups, roles, and Conditional Access foundations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Configuration Summary&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Security groups for role-based access&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Admin roles assigned with least privilege&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;CA policies for MFA, compliant devices, and risky sign-ins&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;PowerShell Commands Used&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-powershell&quot;&gt;
Connect-MgGraph -Scopes &#39;Policy.ReadWrite.ConditionalAccess&#39;,&#39;Directory.ReadWrite.All&#39;
Get-MgIdentityConditionalAccessPolicy | Select-Object DisplayName,State,Conditions
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Validation Steps&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Test MFA prompts, sign-in risk behavior, and device compliance gate to Exchange/Teams.&lt;/p&gt;
